Former child star Merica Monamodi had a complete turnaround in her career and personal life after she ditched the entertainment industry to go teach in North Korea. Merica who is also a Youtuber shared in a video on Youtube with how she lost weight on a Keto diet mixed with fasting. “Keto diet mixed with Intermittent fasting is your best friend. Quit carbs including sweet potato, brown rice etc. Quit junk… NO MORE SUGAR!!! Cut down on the alcohol. I only consume gin & tonic, vodka & soda water, dry white wine. NO MORE CIDERS & BEERS.,” she shared her secrets. WATCH VIDEO BELOW: 